    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## **AI Student Inquiry Automation Flow**\n1. User sends a message.\n\n2. AI replies like a receptionist.\n3. AI gets course info from Google Sheet name is Institute Q&A Tool.\n\n4. AI remembers conversation.\n5. AI collects name, email, phone, course.\n\n6. Chat is saved in sheet name is Chat Query.\n7. Checks if email is given.\n8. Prepares user details.\n9. Saves lead in sheet name is Leads.\n\n10. Creates email message.\n\n11. Sends email to student.\n12. Sends lead info to counselor.",
        "height": 448,
        "width": 2256
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        -2112,
        -2816
      ],
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "id": "40f00487-13b0-4ab2-8096-80e485bb5fb0",
      "name": "Sticky Note1"
    },
    {
