    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## **Lead Scoring & Email Automation Flow**\n1. Workflow starts manually.\n\n2. Chat data is fetched from Google Sheet name is Chat Query.\n3. All user messages are combined into one text.\n4. Important info is extracted from user message.\n5. System calculates lead score based on keywords.\n\n6. Lead is classified as HOT, WARM, or COLD.\n\n7. HOT leads are marked high priority.\n8. WARM leads are marked medium priority.\n9. COLD leads are marked low priority.\n\n10. HOT leads get strong follow-up email.\n11. WARM leads get normal course info email.\n12. COLD leads get reminder/re-engagement email.",
